title: Basalt to Bay in the awards
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Basalt to Bay in the awards Basalt to Bay in the awards Next Story Prev Story 3 hrs ago Read more: Warrnambool Standard 
The Basalt to Bay Landcare Network has won a Victorian Landcare award to promote the economic benefits of shelter belts of native vegetation. THE awards and scholarships keep coming for the local Basalt to Bay Landcare Network that covers the Warrnambool and Moyne local government areas.
